Parliament, Sunday, 25 August 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Agriculture, Land Reform and Rural Development will be conducting an oversight visit in KwaZulu-Natal.     ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON AGRICULTURE, LAND REFORM AND RURAL DEVELOPMENT, INKOSI ZWELIVELILE MANDELA. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Sureshinee GovenderParliamentary Communication ServicesTel: 021 403 2239Cell: 081 704 1109E-mail: sugovender@parliament.gov.za The copy of an Act of Parliament signed by the President is the official version of that Act and is given to the Constitutional Court for safekeeping.Read more